 '"'||v2.city_name||'"', '"'||v3.airport_code||'"', '"'||v4.city_code||'"',
 '"'||v4.city_name||'"', '"'||v5.flight_id||'"',
 '"'||v6.airport_code||'"', '"'||v7.city_code||'"',
 '"'||v7.city_name||'"', v5.stop_number FROM flight v0, airport_service v1,
 city v2, airport_service v3, city v4, flight_stop v5,
